data.title: Atlanta Hawks Roster
data.meta_description: Atlanta Hawks scores, news, schedule, players, stats, rumors, depth charts and more on RealGM.com
data.text:
DeAndre' Bembry was selected as the #21 pick in the First Round of the 2016 NBA Draft by the Atlanta Hawks. DeAndre' Bembry signed a multi-year contract with the Atlanta Hawks on July 14, 2016.

Dennis Schroder was selected as the #17 pick in the First Round of the 2013 NBA Draft by the Atlanta Hawks. Dennis Schroder signed a multi-year contract with the Atlanta Hawks on July 10, 2013. Dennis Schroder signed a multi-year extension with the Atlanta Hawks on October 26, 2016.

Draft Rights to Mike Muscala, the #14 pick in the Second Round of the 2013 NBA Draft, were acquired by the Atlanta Hawks from the Dallas Mavericks on June 27, 2013. Mike Muscala signed a multi-year contract with the Atlanta Hawks on February 27, 2014.

Draft Rights to Taurean Prince, the #12 pick in the First Round of the 2016 NBA Draft, were acquired by the Atlanta Hawks from the Utah Jazz on July 7, 2016. Taurean Prince signed a multi-year contract with the Atlanta Hawks on July 14, 2016.

Mike Dunleavy was acquired in a trade by the Atlanta Hawks from the Cleveland Cavaliers on January 7, 2017.

Tim Hardaway Jr. was acquired in a trade by the Atlanta Hawks from the New York Knicks on June 26, 2015.

Ersan Ilyasova was acquired in a trade by the Atlanta Hawks from the Philadelphia Sixers on February 22, 2017.

Thabo Sefolosha was acquired in a sign and trade by the Atlanta Hawks from the Oklahoma City Thunder on July 15, 2014.

Kent Bazemore signed a multi-year contract with the Atlanta Hawks on September 10, 2014. Kent Bazemore re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Atlanta Hawks on July 7, 2016.

Malcolm Delaney signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Atlanta Hawks on July 14, 2016.

Dwight Howard signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Atlanta Hawks on July 12, 2016.

Kris Humphries signed a contract with the Atlanta Hawks on March 1, 2016. Kris Humphries re-signed to a contract as a free agent with the Atlanta Hawks on July 14, 2016.

Ryan Kelly signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Atlanta Hawks on February 24, 2017.

Paul Millsap signed a multi-year contract with the Atlanta Hawks on July 10, 2013. Paul Millsap re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Atlanta Hawks on July 9, 2015.
